        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Joint Chiefs Landscape Restoration Partnership Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Agriculture (USDA) to establish a Joint Chiefs Landscape Restoration Partnership program to improve the health and resilience of forest landscapes across National Forest System lands and state, tribal, and private lands. Activities under the program may include reducing the risk of wildfire, protecting water quality and supply, or improving wildlife habitat for at-risk species.</p>    ]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
